name: Global X Mid-Term Government Bond Premium Yield ETF
longDescription: Fund Invests in  high monthly distributions of interest income and option premiums. To generate premiums and reduce volatility, PAYL will employ a dynamic option program. PAYL seeks to hedge any foreign currency exposure back to the Canadian dollar. PAYL seeks to provide (a) exposure to the performance of government debt securities, primarily issued by the Government of Canada, generally targeting a duration over ten years.
